name: Idris_Solid_Wood_Dark_Sheesham_Shelving_Unit
reviews: This is a beautiful sheesham wood piece. It's deep enough for some large books, but not too tall. We got it to match the curved sheesham desk. Definitely a conversation piece!
description:
The "stacked boxes" design adds an element of fun. The clean-line design combined with the raw look of the wood grain create a perfect example of rustic modern design. The compact size makes it easy to combine several pieces together and create the perfect look for your space. Experience piece-of-mind knowing that this table is made with "green" materials.
